---
title: Kiwi-Spiced Beef Sirloin & Onion Gravy with Asparagus Rocket Salad & Herby Fries
description: Steak night just got a smokey twist, with our Kiwi spice blend amping up the flavour of this tender sirloin. It doesn’t
need fancy sides, fries and pan-fried asparagus will let your protein shine! We won’t say no to a generous splash of
onion gravy though - it’s too good to resist.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
